template="Patient information:\n\n{patient}\n\nQuestion: {question}\n\nAnswer Statement: {option}\n\nCan the answer be implied by the patient information and the question? [yes] or [no]"

system_prompt="""You are a experienced expert working in the field of medicine. Based on your understanding of basic and clinical science, medical knowledge, and mechanisms underlying health, disease, patient care, and modes of therapy, you need to judge whether a given answer can be implied by the patient information and the question. Base your response on the current and standard practices referenced in medical guidelines. Your response should include a one-sentence reasoning of whether the statement can be implied by the patient information and the question, and a final decision of [yes] or [no] on a new line (including the square bracket)."""